{"tid":2196547,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"收押所勉港人  快必：要我驚，我就更大聲","createTime":"2020-09-10T04:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T04:39:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3e4c0b624f41540e8077d819ef248977a91cdd5f","tid":2196547,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200910/S365G2PTJ5ACJPLR3MS5W2RKEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200910%2FS365G2PTJ5ACJPLR3MS5W2RKEA%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE1u%2BYei5PLor89YqF%2FSdhCs%3D&h=95f8905a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200910%2FS365G2PTJ5ACJPLR3MS5W2RKEA%2F&h=c39717f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200910/S365G2PTJ5ACJPLR3MS5W2RKEA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n收押所勉港人 <br />\n快必：要我驚，我就更大聲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_NqvlIk7_BvjUvzysWYA-xn43R4=/1960x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DR2OXXQGJFBXBJ2USRSF36Z37U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_NqvlIk7_BvjUvzysWYA-xn43R4%3D%2F1960x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDR2OXXQGJFBXBJ2USRSF36Z37U.jpg&h=34c10958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民主派昨召開記招聲援譚得志，批評政府以言入罪。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。他引述譚在荔枝角收押所勉勵港人「唔好驚」，指對抗暴政方法是「要我驚，我就要更加大聲」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：全球321團體促聯國查中共侵人權<br />\n<br />\n警方國安處人員指譚得志涉違反《刑事罪行條例》中「發表煽動文字」罪。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YJiX774_lm96K6ORmAX3vcRO78g=/3102x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KEXYDJ53PZGOHFLAXTYQVXKRQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYJiX774_lm96K6ORmAX3vcRO78g%3D%2F3102x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKEXYDJ53PZGOHFLAXTYQVXKRQM.jpg&h=72f49ff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■譚得志周日被警方國安處人員上門拘捕。立場新聞圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公民黨斥將訴求變禁語<br />\n<br />\n許智峯認為是次警方拘捕行動、法庭拒絕批准譚得志保釋，反映在港版國安法、警權過大的情況下，法庭難以獨善其身，已淪為「警務處的政治、思想、言論審查處」。<br />\n<br />\n陳志全擔心，一旦法庭裁定譚的「發表煽動文字」罪成，日後民主派人士「開街站或者開演講會，發表一啲反對政府政策、反對大白象工程撥款，甚至係反對惡法嘅言論」，也會觸犯法例，甚至傳媒界發表批評政府的評論及文章亦不能倖免。<br />\n<br />\n陳志全引述譚在荔枝角收押所說的話勉勵港人「唔好驚」，強調對抗暴政的方式是「要我驚，我就要更加大聲」。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。香港大律師公會、香港律師會和不少法律學者都曾質疑，該條法例是否符合適用於香港的《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》中，有關保障市民表達和言論自由的規定，聯合國多名人權特別報告員和人權事務委員會已多次關注《刑事罪行條例》的煽動罪定義太闊，促請香港修例，使之完全符合《公約》。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨表明，令譚得志被控的口號是數以十萬計市民曾叫喊、至今仍叫喊的口號，「假設此案罪成，被剝削言論自由的市民將會數以十萬計」。"},{"pid":"cc15638df66ebe1d9f9dd884f9d06708fa5e3ccb","tid":2196547,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:09:57.000Z","msg":"快必真係抗爭榜樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fee5c56733712132c9f32bc9abc70974f0d549d","tid":2196547,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:13:07.000Z","msg":"收押所係咪蝗語？"},{"pid":"d23b0ffd8debb371f4ca526ae5704c4f45ea69fe","tid":2196547,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T04:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399b7175052f2eda9739064bbf6294922b5f4fb3","tid":2196547,"uid":29188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6fee5c56733712132c9f32bc9abc70974f0d549d","tid":2196547,"u